dct_title_s: Tabula terræ Novæ Zemblæ, in qua Fretum Sinusq[ue] Waigats item Ora Littorlis Tartariæ atq Russiæ
dct_description_sm: Bar scale on map given in "Theutsche meylen".
Decorative cartouches, compass roses, rhumb lines, figures, fort, ships, seals, ice bergs, sea monsters.
Shows Barentsz's cabin on Nova Zembla.
Verso contains map of "Insula Kildyn" and "Cola" and descriptive text in German.
Appears in de Bry's Petits voyages, part X (Indiae Orientalis), 1613.
